  <brief_title>4G/5G Polymorphism of Plasminogen Activator Inhibitor-1 Gene and Disseminated Intravascular Coagulation in Severe Sepsis and Septic Shock</brief_title>
  <official_title>Incidence and Prognosis of Disseminated Intravscular Coagulation in Patients Severe Sepsis and Septic Shock; Association With 4G/5G Polymorphism of PAI-1 Gene</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
